          <div class='pagegroup'><a href='http://sli.ics.uci.edu/Classes'>Classes</a> /</div>
          <h1 class='pagetitle'>CS274b: Learning in Graphical Models</h1></div>
<!--PageText-->
<div id='wikitext'>
<div class='Work' style='float:right; padding:5px; border:2px solid black; background-color:#f0f8ff' >
<p><span style='font-size:144%'><strong>Assignments and Exams:</strong></span>
</p>
<table border='0' cellspacing='3' ><tr ><td  align='left'><a class='urllink' href='http://sli.ics.uci.edu/Classes/2016S-274b?action=download&amp;upname=HW1.pdf' rel='nofollow'>HW1</a>, <a class='urllink' href='http://sli.ics.uci.edu/Classes/2016S-274b?action=download&amp;upname=HW1c.zip' rel='nofollow'>Data</a></td><td  align='left'>Due 4/15</td><td >&nbsp;</td><td >&nbsp;</td><td >&nbsp;</td></tr>
<tr ><td  align='left'><a class='urllink' href='http://sli.ics.uci.edu/Classes/2016S-274b?action=download&amp;upname=HW2.pdf' rel='nofollow'>HW2</a>, <a class='urllink' href='http://sli.ics.uci.edu/Classes/2016S-274b?action=download&amp;upname=HW2c.zip' rel='nofollow'>Code &amp; Data</a></td><td  align='left'>Due 4/29</td><td >&nbsp;</td><td >&nbsp;</td><td >&nbsp;</td></tr>
